---
const taskSignals = [
  '跨多个文件或目录',
  '需要分阶段执行',
  '涉及迁移、重构或规则调整',
  '容易被上下文遗漏',
];

const lightweightSignals = [
  '只改一处文案或样式',
  '没有明显阶段状态',
  '失败不会产生副作用',
  '能快速验证清楚',
];
---

<section class="agent-workflow-tree" aria-label="Agent 工作流选择决策树">
  <header class="tree-header">
    <span class="tree-eyebrow">DECISION TREE</span>
    <h2>Agent 工作流怎么选？</h2>
    <p>不是所有任务都要上复杂流程。先判断任务规模、状态风险和副作用，再决定直接做、写 brief，还是建立 TASK.md。</p>
  </header>

  <div class="tree-stage start-stage">
    <article class="tree-card start-card">
      <span class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">👤</span>
      <span class="card-kicker">START</span>
      <h3>收到一个任务</h3>
      <p>先不要急着抽象，先判断它到底是小改、流程任务，还是多阶段任务。</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="tree-stage decision-stage">
    <article class="tree-card question-card">
      <span class="card-kicker">Q1</span>
      <h3>只是小修小补？</h3>
      <p>例如改一句话、调整一个样式、补一个小判断。</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="branch-grid">
    <article class="tree-card answer-card yes-card">
      <span class="branch-label">是</span>
      <h3>直接改，不引入 TASK.md</h3>
      <p>保持最小改动，最后说明改了什么、怎么验证。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="tree-card answer-card no-card">
      <span class="branch-label">否</span>
      <h3>继续判断任务规模</h3>
      <p>不要因为任务看起来复杂，就立刻上重流程。</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="tree-stage decision-stage">
    <article class="tree-card question-card">
      <span class="card-kicker">Q2</span>
      <h3>跨文件、跨阶段、容易丢状态？</h3>
      <p>例如规则迁移、内容重构、组件改造、长任务分批执行。</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="branch-grid">
    <article class="tree-card answer-card yes-card strong-card">
      <span class="branch-label">是</span>
      <h3>先建立 TASK.md</h3>
      <p>写清目标、阶段、验收标准、当前进度和风险点。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="tree-card answer-card no-card">
      <span class="branch-label">否</span>
      <h3>用轻量 brief 即可</h3>
      <p>先写目标、边界和验证点，不额外制造维护文件。</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="tree-stage decision-stage">
    <article class="tree-card question-card">
      <span class="card-kicker">Q3</span>
      <h3>会产生副作用吗？</h3>
      <p>例如写文件、删内容、发消息、推送、批量处理数据、操作页面后台。</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="branch-grid final-branches">
    <article class="tree-card answer-card danger-card">
      <span class="branch-label">是</span>
      <h3>加日志、验证和人工确认</h3>
      <p>副作用必须可追踪，失败分支不能被隐藏。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="tree-card answer-card yes-card">
      <span class="branch-label">否</span>
      <h3>保持流程可读</h3>
      <p>用普通正文、列表或 Mermaid 表达清楚即可。</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="signal-grid">
    <article class="signal-card task-card">
      <h3>适合 TASK.md 的信号</h3>
      <ul>
        {taskSignals.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
      </ul>
    </article>
    <article class="signal-card light-card">
      <h3>不该复杂化的信号</h3>
      <ul>
        {lightweightSignals.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
      </ul>
    </article>
  </div>

  <footer class="tree-footer">
    <strong>最终输出标准</strong>
    <span>目标清楚 · 边界清楚 · 失败可见 · 验证可复现</span>
  </footer>
</section>

